<h1><b>sql-string. Getting date in DBMS-style format
<br />
</b></h1>
<br />
<mono><b>^date.sql-string[]
<br />
</b><normal>
<br />
Method transforms the date into </mono><mono><b>YYYY-MM-DD&nbsp;HH:MM:SS</b></mono><normal> format, used by DBMS for storing dates. Using this method you can add date values to DB without any additional transformations.
